To release a new version of OPKGC, the following is required:
* Update the ChangeLog file.
* Update the version in AC_INIT in configure.ac.
* Update the version in src/opkgc.
* Update the spec file and the Debian changelog in ../packages.
* Create a new tarball using make dist.
* Create new binary packages copying the proper file in the current directory
  and running the proper scripts.
